title: TOOL 10,000 days (synchronized, full version).mp3
description:
This is synchronized, full version

 of Tool's "10,000 days" track...



 The quality isn't so great (MP3, 128kb)

 and there could be a few ms error signal as well. 

 Anyway - when you'll hear it -

 you'll know how to "create it" on your own...

 ...with perfect imposition/infliction and better quality.



 Dedicated for people who loves this outstanding album

 and still didn't know about this "version" (if any...).

 This file was created in May, 2006.



 Enjoy and >> keep seeding << please, for some time.

 Otherwise PPL will have to wait for a long time...



 Thanks.
